'''Strike the Moons [[Flightknife]]''' was a unit of [[Adumar/Legends|Adumari]] [[Blade-32 superiority fighter]]s, commanded by [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Liak ke Mattino]] in [[13 ABY/Legends|13 ABY]]. They were the first Adumari unit to challenge [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]]' [[Red Flight]] in an honor duel, using only simulated lasers and pigment-filled missiles. The pilots learned several lessons from Wedge's Red Flight following the action. Several days later, ''Strike the Moons'' helped Red Flight escape from [[Cartann]] by firing upon [[Lords of Dismay Flightknife]], justifying their action as refusing to allow "some honor-grubber" stop Wedge. They presumably flew under Cartann's colors during the following engagement; their captain, ke Mattino, was shot down and killed during that time.

